[Name] PrBoom
[Summary] Port of the Doom engine.
[Description] An open-source port of the Doom engine that attempts to be faithful to the original, while fixing bugs and providing new features. Plays Doom, Ultimate Doom, Doom II, and any other games on the original engine. Requires original WAD files. Shareware WAD files can be downloaded from http://www.doomworld.com/files/shareware.shtml  
[License] GNU Public Licence, Version 2
[Homepage] http://prboom.sourceforge.net/
